'''Keisha Castle-Hughes''' is an Australian-born New Zealand actress. She has appeared in films such as ''[[Wikipedia:Whale Rider|Whale Rider]]'', ''[[Wikipedia:Star Wars Episode III: Revenge of the Sith|Star Wars Episode III: Revenge of the Sith]]'', ''[[Wikipedia:The Nativity Story|The Nativity Story]]'', and ''[[wikipedia:Piece of My Heart (film)|Piece of My Heart]]''.

She received an [[Wikipedia:Academy Award for Best Actress|Academy Award nomination&nbsp;for Best Actress]] for her debut performance inÂ â€‹''[[Wikipedia:Whale Rider|Whale Rider]]''â€‹, and at the time was, at age 13, the youngest person in history to be nominated for the award until 2012, with 9 year old [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/QuvenzhanĂŠ_Wallis QuvenzhanĂŠ Wallis], nominated for [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Beasts_of_the_Southern_Wild Beasts of the Southern Wild].

In ''[[Game of Thrones (TV series)|Game of Thrones]]'', she will be playing the part of [[Obara Sand]] in the [[Season 5 |fifth season]].
